    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "さーて、お仕事お仕事……\nあっ、ライブ直前のkanaの自撮り上げなきゃ",
      "startTime": 5.162820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ直前！　みんなに会えるの楽しみでーす\nっと、投稿",
      "startTime": 13.962820522,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 453.3333332999998,
          "startTime": 9.6161538553
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2133.3333332999996,
          "startTime": 16.0961538553
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "おおっ、どんどんコメントがついてる\nいいぞ……もっとだ、もっと来い……！",
      "startTime": 20.5543487787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、本番直前なのに余裕ですね",
      "startTime": 25.0294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "余裕あったらいけない？",
      "startTime": 28.8961538553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、普通は緊張感というか……多少なりとも\nぴりぴりした空気になるんじゃないかと",
      "startTime": 34.362820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "別に。やることやってんだから\n今更、緊張なんてする訳ないっしょ",
      "startTime": 39.9961538553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "kanaの頭の中にあるのは、成功するイメージだけ\n絶対にこのステージを成功させる。いや、させて当然",
      "startTime": 48.5294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "それにさ、ギャラもらってるんだから\n仕事はきっちりやんなきゃじゃん？",
      "startTime": 56.762820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "つくづく思いますけど……\nkanaさんのメンタル、鋼みたいですね",
      "startTime": 61.062820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　今更分かったの？\nkanaのアイドルとしての覚悟とプライド",
      "startTime": 67.8294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "kanaは、スリクスは、二度と負けない\n観客動員数でも、ライブバトルでも",
      "startTime": 77.3961538553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "だからkanaはスリクスを続けてるの",
      "startTime": 82.0294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……サニーピースへのリベンジのためですか？",
      "startTime": 84.8294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ。どうだろ\nもう誰にも負けたくないってのは、間違いないけど",
      "startTime": 92.0294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "どうせやるんだったら、勝って一番になりたいじゃん\nkana達はそれが出来るくらい、超強いんだから",
      "startTime": 100.962820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "それに、mihoもfranも全然好きじゃないけど\nステージの上のあいつらだけは、信用してるから",
      "startTime": 109.4294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんだかんだ言って）\n（メンバーのことは認めてるんだな……）",
      "startTime": 115.4294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "ほんっとうに、ぜんっぜん、好きじゃないけど",
      "startTime": 118.062820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこは強調しなくても……とにかく当面は\nみなさんなりのやり方を見守ることにします",
      "startTime": 126.9294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今までのアイドルにはない何かを感じますから",
      "startTime": 129.7961538553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　{user}が担当してきた連中と\nスリクスを一緒にしないでくれる？",
      "startTime": 136.7294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "実力も、プロとしての覚悟も、全然違うんだから！\n……さて、そろそろ仕事の時間。行ってくるわ",
      "startTime": 145.4663006341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "後でSNSに上げるんだから\nkanaの可愛いところ、沢山撮ってよね",
      "startTime": 153.462820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "任せて下さい。しっかりカメラに収めますから",
      "startTime": 157.0294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "当然。さっきは全然役に立たなかったんだから\nせいぜい頑張んなよ？",
      "startTime": 164.862820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました、今でも結構頑張ってはいるんですが",
      "startTime": 166.9294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan019.m4a",
      "text": "まだ足りませ～ん。全然足りませ～ん\nこんなレベルじゃ困るんですけど～",
      "startTime": 175.9294871886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan020.m4a",
      "text": "kanaはナンバーワンアイドルになるんだよ？",
      "startTime": 179.062820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-kan021.m4a",
      "text": "だからあんたにも、ナンバーワンの\nマネージャーになってもらわないと困るんだから",
      "startTime": 185.462820522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。なってみせますよ",
      "startTime": 188.9294871886,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4066.6666667000018,
          "startTime": 192.9961538553
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
